        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2360_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(2)把该书店5月份这四周销售的图书本数按从少到多的顺序排列。(2分)",
