          0.3354123354123354
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2360_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(2)现在购买一台冰箱和一台洗衣机一共要花多少钱？ (3分)",
