        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2360_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(3)卖出图书的数量最多的一周比最少的一周大约多多少本书？(2分)",
