        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2360_20",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "5.下面是三种电子产品的价格情况。（10分）",
        "bbox": [
          0.5147426286856571,
          0.46292446292446293,
          0.7256371814092953,
