        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2360_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "3.水果店里的苹果、香蕉、梨各有多少千克?将水果的名称填人下表中。（6分）",
